OnAction (GUI item event)
=========================

On most item types, called when the user clicks on a [GUI\_items.html GUI item] with the mouse.

On [EditDef\_(GUI\_item\_type).html editDefs], this is called when the text changes.

On [ChoiceDef\_(GUI\_item\_type).html choiceDefs], this is called when the selected option changes.

